testcase.classname: I would like to have a page to register as a visitor
testcase.name: TC13 : It must be verified that the registration process can be completed by filling in the mandatory fields in the form (firstname/lastname/address textboxes).
testcase.system-out: * The visitor enters the site with the given "Url"..........................passed * Click on the Get Started Button Link on the Home Page.....................passed * A unique username with at least 6 characters is entered in the Username box..passed * Valid e-mail information containing the @ sign is entered into the e-mail text box.passed * Country selection is made from the Country menu...........................passed * A unique phone number of maximum 14 digits is entered into the phone textbox..passed * A 6-digit password containing at least one uppercase letter, one number, lowercase letter and character is entered into the Password textbox..passed * The specified password is entered in the Confirm textbox..................passed * click on the i agree button...............................................passed * click on the register button..............................................passed * Name is entered in the firstname box......................................passed * Surname is entered in the lastname box....................................passed * Address is entered in the address box.....................................passed * State is entered in the state box.........................................passed * zip code entered in zip code box..........................................passed * Country is entered in the city box........................................passed * Click on the submit button................................................passed * Verify that registration process completed successfully appears...........passed * Close the page............................................................passed
